<div  class="item" id="author-instruction">
    <p class="header">INSTRUCTIONS TO AUTHORS</p>
    <p class="item">Please read and follow these instructions carefully. The Editors 
        reserve the right to return manuscripts that are not prepared according to the instructions.
    </p>
    <p class="header" >SUBMISSION OF MANUSCRIPTS</p>
    <p class="item">
        Manuscripts must be previously unpublished, not under consideration for publication 
        elsewhere. It should not then be published elsewhere in the same form. 
        Copyright-holder's permission must have been obtained prior to submission.
    </p>
    <p class="header" >COPYRIGHT</p>
    <p class="item">
        By submitting an article for publication you confirm that you are the corresponding/submitting 
        author. We may retain your email address for the purpose of communicating with you about the article. 
        You agree to notify us immediately if your details change. 
        If your article is accepted for publication we will contact you using the email address you have used in 
        the registration process.
    </p>
    <p class="header" >GENERAL FORMAT</p>
    <p class="item">
        Papers must be clearly written in English. The manuscript should contain the following information: 
        title, complete list of authors and their affiliations and addresses, the main text include figures, tables and references.
        Author postal code, e-mail addresses, and telephone and fax numbers should be provided.
    </p>
</div>